{"about_the_game":"You  have 24 hours to out-muscle the competition to become mayor. <br />\r\nAlso, the world might be ending??<br />\r\nWho cares?! Let's FLEX!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHeart is Muscle is a RPG-VN hybrid that takes inspiration from the SaGa games, in which the plot continues to progress, regardless if you're there or not. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures: <br />\r\n- 7 endings to find, including an unlockable epilogue<br />\r\n- Bake cookies (to restore HP)<br />\r\n- Pet a dog (by punching it). (It's not hurt, I swear)<br />\r\n- Talk and trade with 12 different NPCs<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-----<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHello! I made Heart is Muscle as a way to teach myself Unity and was so happy with the results I've since decided to port it to steam! I hope you have as much fun going around punching things as I did making it. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you so much for looking at (and possibly playing!?) my game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Heiden","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1665751376","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978970/page.bg.jpg?t=1665751376","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978970/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1665751376","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978970/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1665751376","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2144140,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"You  have 24 hours to out-muscle the competition to become mayor. <br />\r\nAlso, the world might be ending??<br />\r\nWho cares?! Let's FLEX!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHeart is Muscle is a RPG-VN hybrid that takes inspiration from the SaGa games, in which the plot continues to progress, regardless if you're there or not. <br />\r\n<br />\r